These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, aquamarine
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Color   | aquamarine | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, azalea
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Flower   | begonia | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Sport   | tennis | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, davidoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Cigar   | davidoff | chaman |

 #################################

 
